cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.ST, cs.CY

This paper discusses the publication trends of different countries and the use of databases for measurement. The most relevant sub-category is cs.DL (Digital Libraries) as it deals with the organization, management, and access to digital information. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it talks about retrieving sets of documents and comparing publication trends. Additionally, it touches upon social networks and their impact (cs.SI), statistical analysis (cs.ST), and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it mentions the dynamics of databases used for measurement.
